trans-unit.source: The ID of the client component.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor.ClientID%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor> class always returns the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor.ElementID%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor.ClientID%2A> propriedade o <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor> classe sempre retorna o valor da <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor.ElementID%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.target: A ID de HTML do objeto de controle do cliente.

trans-unit.target: Obtém a ID da instância <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: The ID of the current <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptControlDescriptor" /> instance, if set; otherwise, an empty string ("").
